### Footnotes

<span id="fn_1462"></span>[337:1](sbe24160.htm#fr_1473.md) See Pahl. Vend.
VII, 65-71.

<span id="fn_1463"></span>[337:2](sbe24160.htm#fr_1474.md) Lp, B29 have
'for.'

<span id="fn_1464"></span>[337:3](sbe24160.htm#fr_1475.md) La has sâl, and
B29 san for 'year;' Lp has 'that when the bê*s* and locust come
profusely.' The bê*s* may be either a poisonous plant (*Napellus
Moysis*), or 'distress.'

